OL,3,CSecond man charged with assisting
OL,4,CDaniel Khalife after prison escape
OL,6,FA second man has been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with helping former soldier
OL,8,FDaniel Khalife escape from HMP
OL,9,FWandsworth.
OL,11,FAdeel Khan, 30, from Waltham Forest,
OL,12,Fis accused of aiding Khalife's
OL,13,FSeptember 2023 prison escape, during
OL,14,Fwhich Khalife secured himself to the
OL,15,Fbottom of a food delivery truck, using
OL,16,Fa sling made of prison trousers and
OL,17,Fcarabiners.
