OL,3,CSecond man charged with assisting
OL,4,CDaniel Khalife after prison escape
OL,6,FKhalife spent four days on the run
OL,7,Fafter using prison trousers to fasten
OL,8,Fhimself to a vehicle and leave the
OL,9,Fsite.
OL,11,FAdeel Khan has also been charged with
OL,12,Fpossession of a phone in prison, the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,15,FHe was charged earlier this month and
OL,16,Fis due to appear at Westminster
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday.
