OL,3,CSecond man charged with assisting
OL,4,CDaniel Khalife after prison escape
OL,6,FLast week, Imran Chowdhury, 25, from
OL,7,FChingford, east London, was also
OL,8,Fcharged with assisting Khalife. He
OL,9,Fappeared at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt on January 7, where he denied
OL,11,Fthe charge.
OL,13,FChowdhury has been bailed and will
OL,14,Fappear at Snaresbrook Crown Court on
OL,15,FFebruary 4.
OL,17,FDaniel Khalife, 23, was convicted in
OL,18,FNovember 2024 of spying for Iran
OL,19,Ffollowing a trial. Jurors at Woolwich
OL,20,FCrown Court found he had breached the
OL,21,FOfficial Secrets and Terrorism Acts.
