OL,6,FHe had already admitted to escaping
OL,7,Ffrom Wandsworth Prison after initially
OL,8,Fdenying the offence, and then changing
OL,9,Fhis plea part-way through his trial.
OL,11,FKhalife was cleared of carrying out a
OL,12,Fbomb hoax at the Army barracks where
OL,13,Fhe had been based.
